    "title": "Collingwood Hospitality Group: $2.1M Refinancing Saves $185K Annually",
    "date": "2026-01-22",
    "description": "How a Melbourne restaurant group refinanced expensive bank debt and high-interest equipment loans, reducing interest costs by $185K annually and freeing up $45K monthly cash flow.",
    "category": "Case Studies",
